# Quality Gates (质量门禁)

Scope: all DTS CI/CD pipelines

## PR Gate (every pull request)

- [ ] Lint passes (ruff/checkstyle/golangci-lint/eslint)
- [ ] Unit tests pass (per-service)
- [ ] Build succeeds (per-service)
- [ ] No new critical/high vulnerabilities (dependency scan)
- [ ] API spec backward-compatible (proto breaking change detection)
- [ ] Code review approved (minimum 1 reviewer)

## Nightly Gate (daily on develop branch)

- [ ] All PR Gate checks
- [ ] Integration tests pass (per-service with Testcontainers)
- [ ] E2E core tests pass (3 critical paths)
- [ ] AI evaluation regression check (accuracy >= baseline)
- [ ] Docker image build succeeds for all services
- [ ] Helm chart lint passes

## Release Gate (before version tag)

- [ ] All Nightly Gate checks
- [ ] Full E2E suite passes (all 5 critical paths)
- [ ] AI evaluation full suite passes (all capabilities)
- [ ] Performance benchmark: API P95 < 200ms, AI P95 < 5s
- [ ] Offline bundle build succeeds
- [ ] Offline deployment smoke test passes
- [ ] Changelog and version bumps reviewed
- [ ] Security audit: no critical CVEs in dependencies

## Hotfix Gate (emergency fixes)

- [ ] Unit tests pass for changed files
- [ ] Integration test for affected service
- [ ] Targeted E2E for affected path
- [ ] Peer review by senior engineer
